---
// Process component showing our methodology
---

<section id="process" class="process section-animate">
  <div class="section-container">
    <div class="process-layout">
      <div class="process-text">
        <h2>From bottleneck to business win in 4–8 weeks.</h2>
        <p class="section-description">We've productized our approach so you always know where you stand.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="process-grid">
        <div class="step card-animate">
          <div class="icon-placeholder">1</div>
          <h3>Discovery Sprint (1–2 Weeks)</h3>
          <p>We map your workflows and pinpoint the 3–5 highest-ROI fixes. If we don't find opportunities worth pursuing, you pay nothing.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="step card-animate">
          <div class="icon-placeholder">2</div>
          <h3>Pilot Build (2–4 Weeks)</h3>
          <p>We design and deploy your first automation — tackling the most painful bottleneck head-on. From day one, it delivers measurable savings.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="step card-animate">
          <div class="icon-placeholder">3</div>
          <h3>Implementation & Enablement</h3>
          <p>We roll out additional solutions, provide your team with simple guides, and stay on hand for refinement — ensuring long-term ROI.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <!-- Background workflow pattern -->
  <div class="workflow-pattern">
    <div class="flow-node node-1"></div>
    <div class="flow-node node-2"></div>
    <div class="flow-node node-3"></div>
    <div class="flow-connection conn-1"></div>
    <div class="flow-connection conn-2"></div>
    <div class="flow-connection conn-3"></div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .process {
    background: 
      linear-gradient(135deg, #F8F9FA 0%, #E8F4FD 100%),
      linear-gradient(45deg, transparent 49%, rgba(0, 123, 255, 0.02) 50%, transparent 51%),
      linear-gradient(-45deg, transparent 49%, rgba(0, 86, 179, 0.02) 50%, transparent 51%);
    background-size: 100% 100%, 80px 80px, 80px 80px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .process-layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 0.8fr 1.2fr;
    gap: 4.2rem;
    align-items: start;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .process-text {
    grid-column: 1;
  }

  .process-text h2 {
    font-size: clamp(2.1rem, 4.2vw, 2.625rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text-dark);
    margin-bottom: 1.575rem;
    line-height: 1.2;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .section-description {
    font-size: clamp(1.26rem, 2.52vw, 1.575rem);
    color: var(--text-dark);
    text-align: left;
    max-width: 400px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .process-grid {
    grid-column: 2;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2.1rem;
  }

  .step {
    text-align: left;
    padding: 2.1rem;
    background-color: white;
    border-radius: 12.6px;
    box-shadow: 0 6.3px 31.5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: none;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .step::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 3px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--accent-blue), var(--electric-blue-dark));
    transform: scaleX(0);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .step:hover::before {
    transform: scaleX(1);
  }

  .step:hover {
    transform: translateY(-8.4px);
    box-shadow: 0 12.6px 42px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
  }

  .icon-placeholder {
    width: 84px;
    height: 84px;
    background: var(--accent-blue);
    color: white;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 2.1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 2.1rem;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .step:hover .icon-placeholder {
    transform: scale(1.05);
  }

  .step h3 {
    text-align: left;
    margin-bottom: 1.575rem;
    font-size: clamp(1.26rem, 2.52vw, 1.575rem);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-dark);
  }

  .step p {
    text-align: left;
    color: var(--text-dark);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin: 0;
    font-size: clamp(1.05rem, 2.1vw, 1.155rem);
  }

  /* Workflow pattern background */
  .workflow-pattern {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .flow-node {
    position: absolute;
    width: 12px;
    height: 12px;
    background: rgba(0, 123, 255, 0.15);
    border-radius: 50%;
    animation: flowPulse 3s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  .node-1 {
    top: 30%;
    left: 15%;
    animation-delay: 0s;
  }

  .node-2 {
    top: 50%;
    left: 50%;
    animation-delay: 1s;
  }

  .node-3 {
    top: 70%;
    right: 20%;
    animation-delay: 2s;
  }

  .flow-connection {
    position: absolute;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(0, 123, 255, 0.1), transparent);
    animation: flowShimmer 4s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  .conn-1 {
    width: 120px;
    height: 2px;
    top: 30%;
    left: 20%;
    transform: rotate(45deg);
    animation-delay: 0s;
  }

  .conn-2 {
    width: 100px;
    height: 2px;
    top: 50%;
    left: 40%;
    transform: rotate(-45deg);
    animation-delay: 1.5s;
  }

  .conn-3 {
    width: 80px;
    height: 2px;
    top: 70%;
    left: 60%;
    transform: rotate(45deg);
    animation-delay: 3s;
  }

  @keyframes flowPulse {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 0.3; transform: scale(1); }
    50% { opacity: 0.8; transform: scale(1.3); }
  }

  @keyframes flowShimmer {
    0% { opacity: 0.2; }
    50% { opacity: 0.6; }
    100% { opacity: 0.2; }
  }

  @media (min-width: 1920px) {
    .step {
      padding: 3.675rem;
    }

    .icon-placeholder {
      width: 105px;
      height: 105px;
      font-size: 2.625rem;
    }

    .section-description {
      font-size: 1.8375rem;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .process-layout {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2.1rem;
    }

    .process-text {
      grid-column: 1;
      grid-row: 1;
    }

    .process-grid {
      grid-column: 1;
      grid-row: 2;
    }

    .section-description {
      font-size: 1.155rem;
      margin-bottom: 3.15rem;
    }

    .step {
      padding: 1.575rem;
    }

    .icon-placeholder {
      width: 47.25px;
      height: 47.25px;
      font-size: 1.155rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.05rem;
    }

    .workflow-pattern {
      display: none;
    }
  }
</style>
